verbose_text: Before therapy, there were no significant differences between group I and II in PH, PO2 and PCO2 (p = 0.294, 0.462, 0.758 respectively), but after 2 weeks of therapy, there were significantly higher PH levels in group I compared with group II (p < 0.001) while there were no significant differences between group I and II regarding PO2 and PCO2.
